{
  "title": "Gently Citrusy Italian Buckwheat Amatriciana",
  "description": "A citrusy and silky one-pot Italian dish featuring buckwheat, this recipe is a macrobiotic-friendly take on the classic Amatriciana, cooked to perfection in a cataplana vessel.",
